Class PostgreSqlSink

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pragmaticminds.crunch.sinks.PostgreSqlSink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AutoCloseable, EventSink<GenericEvent>

    public class PostgreSqlSink
extends Object
implements EventSink<GenericEvent>, Serializable, AutoCloseable
    A Sink for persisting of GenericEvent List in a Events table on a PostgreSQL database.

    Erwin Wagasow Created by Erwin Wagasow on 11.09.2018
